BungieNet.Engine.Contract.Destiny.World..subtitle: Dead Zone Scout
BungieNet.Engine.Contract.Destiny.World..name: Devrim Kay
BungieNet.Engine.Contract.Destiny.World..description: Ever the gentleman sniper, Devrim Kay holds fast in the wilds of the EDZ.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Devrim Kay is no stranger to loss. But the wise know that death never gets easier. Go check in on Devrim to see how he's doing in the wake of Cayde's death.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Devrim Kay

interactions.flavorLineOne: If you ever want to talk, or even just keep an old man company for a bit, Devrim will always be there with a warm cup of tea.
Devrim raises an eyebrow at the gift, but his gratitude seems genuine. He does not take a sip, however.
Devrim is polite as always in his gratitude and waits for you to depart before returning his attention to the window.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Devrim has heard of your victory over Ghaul in the City, and wishes to congratulate you. Speak with him in Trostland.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Devrim Kay

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Devrim congratulates you on your victory over Ghaul.

While the head of the Red Legion has been slain, the Red War continues across the solar system.

"Hello again, Guardian. Getting a feel for the old place? There's constant trouble nipping at our heels out here They don't call it the European Dead Zone for nothing."

As you continue to explore the EDZ, you'll earn XP and rewards for completing adventures, Lost Sectors, public events, world quests, and EDZ bounties.

headerDisplayProperties.description: With the Vanguard back together, more adventures await in the EDZ. Speak with Devrim in Trostland to learn more.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Devrim Kay

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Devrim describes the new challenges you'll face in the wilds of the European Dead Zone

Explore the area for new adventures to complete.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Devrim has noticed your efforts in the European Dead Zone and wishes to speak with you.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Devrim Kay

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Devrim thanks you for the significant progress you've made in the EDZ.

Continue your adventures on the planet to earn his appreciation and rewards.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Devrim is grateful for your many successful adventures in the EDZ. Speak with him in Trostland.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Devrim Kay

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Devrim thanks you for the work you've done in securing the EDZ.

New challenges appear on the horizon, however.

The Fallen stole technology from the Cabal and were using it to make enhanced Ether. Now that they can't make any more, it's time to find any remaining caches of the stuff and destroy them. 

Seek out caches of enhanced Fallen Ether on EDZ and destroy them.

"Stellar job, as always," Devrim says when you return. "I greatly appreciate it."

He glances out his lookout window, and then back at you. "The Festival of the Lost is an important tradition for the people of the City. Our struggles have made us very resilient, very determined to remember the past and to look forward, hopefully, to the future. Guardians like yourself participating in that tradition is important to us." He nods. "Anyway. Here's a little something for your efforts, hm?"

headerDisplayProperties.description: Devrim thanks you for keeping the EDZ safe.
headerDisplayProperties.name: FLASHPOINT: EDZ

interactions.flavorLineOne: Devrim thanks you for keeping the EDZ safe.
The Fallen stole technology from the Cabal and were using it to make enhanced Ether. Now that they can't make any more, it's time to find any remaining caches of enhanced Ether and destroy them.

The communication network is in place, but a nearby Cabal outpost has been jamming all outbound signals. Hawthorne needs to get her message out to the survivors. 

Take Devrim's signal booster and help Hawthorne by completing mission "Combustion."

headerDisplayProperties.description: Devrim has a strange tale to tell of the Fallen.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Enhance!

interactions.flavorLineOne: Oh, Guardian, while you're here The Fallen are up to something nearby, and it might be worth your time to investigate.

Devrim turns from his sniper post, lowering his gun to take the gift you offer. "Thank you," he says, examining it. "Marc does send me care packages sometimes. But it's difficult to get them here. The Fallen activity is quite persistent, and I've been out of ammo for ages."

He glances up. "I like the gifts he sends, but the notes are the real treat. I re-read them sometimes, when it's quiet."

"Ahh, Guardian. Welcome to the EDZ. I can always use your help to keep the local riffraff in check. From the Outskirts to the Gulch, we've got plenty of nasties roaming these hills. And don't get me started on the Cabal's Firebase."

Devrim Kay offers EDZ bounties, quests, and various rewards to Guardians who fight to reclaim the EDZ.

Help Devrim by completing the EDZ adventure, "A New Frontier." Then, complete his other challenges to earn a new reward.
Complete patrols and public events in the EDZ to get Dusklight Crystals and earn rewards from Devrim Kay.
Your reputation in the Crucible precedes you. Take this reward in recognition of your deeds.
Show Devrim Kay proof of your deeds in the EDZ.
Increase your level to claim these rewards.
